[I] GPU and accelerator process monitor

[T] NVTOP stands for Neat Videocard TOP, a (h)top like task monitor for GPUs
[T] and accelerators. It can handle multiple GPUs and print information
[T] about them in a htop-familiar way.

[U] https://github.com/Syllo/nvtop

